  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "They rejected Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "While Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe had called for a meeting of party leaders, it has been reported that the party leaders have decided not to go to that meeting."
      ],
